---
title: Thai-Style Coconut Chickpea Curry with Lime Rice
description: Nothing makes a curry feel ultra luxe and creamy quite like coconut milk. This meal features hearty chickpeas in a fragrant red curry and coconut milk broth with green beans and sweet bell peppers. This flavour bomb is served atop fragrant lime rice and topped with toasted peanuts for a takeout worthy supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-de-pois-chiches-a-la-noix-de-coco-a-la-thailandaise-1869f192.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/thai-style-coconut-chickpea-curry-6332ad568a836693d4054828-3b9e0cde.pdf
